  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0da7 \u0db4\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd6 67\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "67 foreigners arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Sri Lanka Navy, 67 people and a multi-day vessel suspected of attempting to illegally migrate from Sri Lanka to a foreign country by sea were arrested in the Kalmunai area of \u200b\u200bthe East Sea this morning (8).",
        "The Sri Lanka Navy ship Ranarisi inspected a suspected multi-day fishing vessel sailing in the sea area off the Kalmunai area early this morning and found 06 smugglers who were suspected of trying to illegally migrate to a foreign country by sea in that multi-day fishing vessel. The navy also said that 67 people, including 53 men, 6 women and 8 children, were taken into custody along with the multi-day fishing vessel.",
        "The Navy said that the people taken into custody were identified as residents of Mannar, Vavuniya, Mullaitivu, Trincomalee and Batticaloa, aged between one year and 56."
      ],
